FBIS4-6768 "dreas079_i_94007" FBIS-EAS-94-079 Daily Report 23 Apr 1994 Cambodia Sihanouk Appreciative of Leaders' Support Sihanouk Appreciative of Leaders' Support Message to CPP BK2304092394 Phnom Penh National Radio of Cambodia Network in Cambodian 0443 GMT 23 Apr 94 BK2304092394 Phnom Penh National Radio of Cambodia Network in Cambodian 0443 GMT 23 Apr 94 Cambodian BFN ["Message from His Majesty King Norodom Sihanouk Varaman to Samdech Chea Sim, Chairman of the Cambodian People's Party and National Assembly"; dated 22 April -- read by announcer] [Text] Esteemed Samdech: Today, I have received, with the most enthusiastic emotion, the message of support for my 22 April 1994 statement from the entire Cambodian People's Party [CPP] headed by yourself. I would like to express my deepest and warmest thanks to you and the CPP for your constant demonstration of responsibility, which is imbued with fine and sublime patriotism. Samdech and madam, the CPP Standing Committee, and all the CPP members, please accept my deepest and warmest fraternal affection. [Signed] Norodom Sihanouk. [Dated] Phnom Penh, 22 April 1994.
